{"tid":318971,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《狂野時速9》要去太空飆車？","createTime":"2017-07-12T12:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T12:10:06.000Z","uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a475c442268aafd7d551d0b711fff6095948afb","tid":318971,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《狂野時速9》要去太空飆車？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/205014_68321f4c18648dd18bb451dcda267b3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F205014_68321f4c18648dd18bb451dcda267b3f.jpg&h=eeed5c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在接受外媒Screen Rant採訪時， F. Gary Gray被問及下一部電影會不會讓多姆帶隊去太空飆車。對此導演半開玩笑地回答：&ldquo;外太空？聽著，對於這個系列我絕不設限。當我在劇本中讀到潛艇時，我就想著&lsquo;好吧，一切皆有可能&rsquo;。（大笑）你永遠不知道會發生什麼。我還沒在劇本上看到&lsquo;多姆在火星上&rsquo;這樣的想法，不過我得再說一次，你永遠不知道會發生什麼。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/205031_e83420f940c89e85fe4de3058ef37099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F205031_e83420f940c89e85fe4de3058ef37099.jpg&h=8377cbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天已經上過了，下部電影是不是該上太空了？<br />\n<br />\n關於《狂野時速9》的劇情暫無任何消息，不過根據《狂野極速》越來越傾向於&ldquo;超級英雄&rdquo;電影的方向來看，上個太空什麼的，還的確是有可能的事啊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170711/0/5/2/%e7%8b%82%e9%87%8e%e6%99%82%e9%80%9f9-%e8%a6%81%e5%8e%bb%e5%a4%aa%e7%a9%ba%e9%a3%86%e8%bb%8a-7667304.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170711%2F0%2F5%2F2%2F%25e7%258b%2582%25e9%2587%258e%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2580%259f9-%25e8%25a6%2581%25e5%258e%25bb%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e7%25a9%25ba%25e9%25a3%2586%25e8%25bb%258a-7667304.html&d=BQoWquJAM8OzImBuufav%2FHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=75eba3fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170711/0/5/2/%e7%8b%82%e9%87%8e%e6%99%82%e9%80%9f9-%e8%a6%81%e5%8e%bb%e5%a4%aa%e7%a9%ba%e9%a3%86%e8%bb%8a-7667304.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/205430_0de1e329271549f933db03f8247bf45e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F205430_0de1e329271549f933db03f8247bf45e.jpg&h=854445e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cad6b464f5e0f1feb3abb63d9c06bd65289e035b","tid":318971,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"4017b5bbfe0a91ff837eedad7750bb9c5fc21b76","tid":318971,"uid":69607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"f5b7d411f12b89da2aa2873c45ce95f139bc58a9","tid":318971,"uid":46286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"74f9d5899977c9a2e2d688f0427680d04a89e746","tid":318971,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd8a039a5e1eb2e503d87cb29d1ae74e67d021f","tid":318971,"uid":117552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"搵班賊去救世界已經睇到我眼都突晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8324e71a20fb10a54261aabd830a98eb1a5debca","tid":318971,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"特技片upgrade 上科幻片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d3c478fdd0ab1bbfcbb386b79f784f3cbc7ce","tid":318971,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"入黑洞"},{"pid":"16243c4f8486f5f771331957a581d40be4bdd308","tid